 can come later.\",\ntasks/prd.json:281:      \"title\": \"MCP tool discovery and registration\",\ntasks/prd.json:282:      \"description\": \"As a user, I want the agent to discover tools from MCP servers and make them available for use.\",\ntasks/prd.json:284:        \"On startup, read MCP server list from config\",\ntasks/prd.json:285:        \"Call tools/list on each server to get tool definitions\",\ntasks/prd.json:286:        \"Convert MCP tools to ToolPort interface and register in ToolRegistry\",\ntasks/prd.json:287:        \"MCP tool execution forwards via tools/call to the corresponding server\",\ntasks/prd.json:288:        \"Server disconnect auto-removes its tools from registry\",\ntasks/prd.json:295:      \"notes\": \"Add MCP config section to crates/config. Wire discovery in bootstrap. Create McpToolAdapter implementing ToolPort.\",\ntasks/prd.json:302:      \"title\": \"MCP reserved name, capability policy, and lifecycle hooks\",\ntasks/prd.json:303:      \"description\": \"As a developer, I want reserved MCP server names, capability checks, and lifecycle hooks enforced per chicago-mcp-contract.md.\",\ntasks/prd.json:320:      \"notes\": \"Add reserved name list and policy check in mcp-runtime. Wire cleanup hook into agent loop in application crate. ComputerUseLifecycle per chicago-mcp-contract.md.\",\ntasks/prd.json:333:        \"resolve_mode(): determines effective mode from config + session state; result is deterministic\",\ntasks/prd.json:360:        \"ToolRegistry supports filtered view by mode via definitions_for_mode(mode) method\",\ntasks/prd.json:370:      \"notes\": \"Add definitions_for_mode(mode) method to ToolRegistry. Wire into agent loop's tool list construction.\",\ntasks/prd.json:450:      \"notes\": \"Per agent-triggers-contract.md. Depends on remote-runtime crate existing. Wire feature gate in config.\",\ntasks/prd.json:501:        \"Timeout and retry configurable via config\",\ntasks/prd.json:585:        \"Pull → merge → push with 